<p>The setting is striking: terraced gardens cascading down to a private beach, dinner served on candlelit terraces overlooking the Mediterranean, a Michelin-starred restaurant where your rehearsal dinner becomes an event in itself. It's Tuscany's answer to coastal Capri, minus the crowds and Instagram tourists.</p>

